                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "I set the charges that light this whole spire. Timing is everything up here - a fraction late and you are ash."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Third warden. Beat me and you are almost to the apprentice. Ready?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Stand behind the yellow line, please. There is no yellow line anymore. It burned. Stand behind where it used to be."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The Ember Badges arrive in a crate from a supplier out of Deepcore. I sign for the crate. Do not tell the others - they have a whole mythology going."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Scorch - warden of the middle stair",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
